Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有出現在搜索列表上的超頻連接者的名字是叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(492,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終線鋸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來坐在這邊小兄弟有點頭緒的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 其實我平時連接的局域網裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有個會這種把戲的其他連接者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(576,430)}<Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 那傢伙也會用這種手段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽程安排人 你說的最終線鋸等級跟類型是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(443,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等級是6 跟你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色也是名符其實的Rust
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是鐵銹色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙擅長保持中遠距離應戰 專門獵殺近戰型的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說以近戰為主的你 打起來會很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K 那麼就將計就計好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當作給你的情報費
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:00:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他登記成雙人組選手作為誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:00:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…如果說是你的名號的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為誘餌的確是很有誘惑力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個新人沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說他到底是哪裏的誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.06,0:01:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好比我更有名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是復活了的黑暗星雲軍團旗下的白銀之鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(396,430)}<Nega Nebulas>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:56.45,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(663,400)}Determination；決意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8DFCFD&\an5\fs18\frz8\3c&H1919BC&\8frx\pos(389,322)}有人來挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 日珥的「豹」要下場耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs18\pos(317,430)}<Prominence>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她會和黑暗星雲軍團旗下的「鴉」聯手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是組隊 單獨行動的最終線鋸會來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(525,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎飛不起來的傳聞也已經傳得很開了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他知道了 襲擊我們的可能性非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把我秒殺了 接下來就可以和你一對一挑戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要連接局域網的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jigsaw的真身肯定會在這棟樓裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們有沒有辦法找到他真人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許有方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚點我再和你解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非敵人先用 否則千萬不能動用心念系統
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個紅之王也吩咐過了 但為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意是自己心靈裏的洞的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每從裏面抽取力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都會漸漸被拉進那個黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾與之戰鬥過的「災禍之鎧」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造出那個東西的就是初代災星失控的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(520,430)}<Disaster>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以王們都在遏制心意的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像Brain Burst一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心念系統也是一體兩面的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望的另一面是絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 我還是想要相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信心意…相信願望的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…應該說想相信曾經拯救我的Brain Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 Rain說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…也許能改變這個加速世…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K 上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jigsaw估計首先會用遠距離攻擊將我們分開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你開始下手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要和我離開太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛應該就是這傢伙的遠程攻擊輪鋸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不見輪鋸本體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能聽聲反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲過下次攻擊後就一口氣縮短距離
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要猶豫 飛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終線鋸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會放你跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好你是金屬系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 剛才的那是那傢伙的另一招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定位鋸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Still Saw>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種將線鋸固定在空中的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個阻擋對手 再用輪鋸持續進行遠程攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是近戰型的天敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺技計量表借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變形
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上來 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪鋸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Wheel Saw>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然快 但還是比不上子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GJ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good Game
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來 要出店了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話或許可以特定他的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終線鋸的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(355,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才在Jigsawi的左肩上給予了連續打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼深刻的痛覺感受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算回到了現實短時間內還是有影響的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在入口附近 找找看有沒有那種神態的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我一個人在艱苦修行的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在和年長的美女約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是約會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是在對戰聖地約會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是要修行 我也想去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這麼說的話 你不也一直在跟仁子對戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不巧的是她只在最開始和最後階段指導了我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後聽說難得有狩獵Enemy的機會就跑沒影了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 心意系統的修行還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「還遠遠不到能在實戰中使用的程度」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用紅之王的話來說就是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我還是覺得我抓住了些小竅門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 太好了 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春也是 不管結果怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是做得很好 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是等秋葉原BG提供情報了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱那人能通過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春告訴他那傢伙現實世界的特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到Jigsaw的現實身份吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就明天學校見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 事情不會這麼簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我哦 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我會想辦法 把你從那混蛋的威脅中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這就當做我們的出道戰好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青橙鈴音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Lime Bell>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 小千好像和能美聯手在新宿跟人對戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之百的勝率？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是從新宿地區的熟人那裏聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說 如果等黃昏掠奪者必殺技槽集滿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(413,430)}<Dusk Taker>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始飛行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何對戰虛擬角色都遇到他束手無策了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(355,430)}<Duel Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會演變成那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有治癒師充當後盾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠距離飛行型的對戰角色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙完全可以避開同等級 同潛力原則的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美…可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 或許事態會比我們想像的還要嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 我們應該有在心裏這樣想過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能美再怎麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要Master 黑之睡蓮回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(441,430)}<Black Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就可以一刀兩斷 乾脆地解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓 難道你是說會輸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐會輸給能美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想思考這種事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 事到如今必須想好最糟糕的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們在週六之前也得做點力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力所能及的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:12:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只要不探明他如何在對戰表上隱身的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的行動只會束手束腳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pard她們和秋葉原的人都還沒查到什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來找你談談
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要談什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在沒去社團活動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:12:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能美的指示嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的話又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Brain Burst優先於現實世界是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話居然會從小春嘴裏說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有參加社團
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有因為Brain Burst而忘記做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 小春把這些以外的時間全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啦 別那麼認真啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個遊戲而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就上升了兩個等級哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有觀眾說我可能是Brain Burst史上最快的升級速度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍團的邀請也多得我都不知道數量了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(231,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺突然就變成超受歡迎的人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再這樣了 這完全不是你的作風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會聽能美的話是因為那段影像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯的是踩進陷阱的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓能美為所欲為 被抓住弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果連你都被他奪走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白啊 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全不瞭解我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我在加速世界的對戰角色對能美唯命是從
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(480,430)}<Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實世界的我 在這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在小春觸手可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣 你還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是按照我的意志而行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是這樣 以後也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的意志…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 小千到底在想什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你把衣服穿好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也請你相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會輸給能美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被奪走的東西 我也一定會奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我也還有力所能及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想 要好好思考 有田春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從能美出現的所說的一字一句
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他的出現每一個地點 做的每一個動作都想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並加以推測
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是留給你的 最後的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這些 能美是奪不走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定在哪裏會有線索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把那傢伙的秘密和弱點找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美的秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 如果能控制最終線鋸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(497,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個動作是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為他是在驅趕別人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像是看習慣了的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在關閉假想窗口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他沒有戴神經連結裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是其他的電子裝置嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 除了神經連結裝置之外應該沒有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拍的很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是神經連結裝置以前的電子裝置的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最早的VR機器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是2020年代的NERvGear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那個只是完全潛行專用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到拓展現實機能的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神經連結裝置才是第一款
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這兩者之間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還有一個能拓展現實機能的電子裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腦植入芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Brain Implant Chip>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美 這次我要和你做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲結束了 能美征二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 黃昏掠奪者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(444,430)}<Dusk Taker>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 這次你要徹徹底底地認輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你說「我投降了 不要在欺負我了」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了 我只是說你我之間的遊戲已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 你還真是不識時務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和黛學長已經什麼都做不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會打敗黑之王 統治這個學園
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…你只要老實地看著我統治衫並地區就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會讓你如願的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在對戰搜索列表中出現的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你腦中有兩個VR裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違法的大腦植入芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(465,431)}<Brain Implant Chip>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腦植入芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Brain Implant Chip>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是植入在大腦皮層和三重腦髓黏膜的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最外層黏膜裏的小型集成芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有被發現的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常被用在考試時候作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以僅僅三年 就被嚴禁生產的違法電子裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平時就是用大腦植入芯片連接校內網絡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並用這個上課和參加考試
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在對戰的瞬間才連接上神經連結裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(590,430)}<Neural Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你不出現在對戰搜索列表中的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你植入那個東西的事曝光的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會被勒令退學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芯片也會被處理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以為你是豬 原來你是老鼠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是四處亂竄 讓我心煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始你就應該先滅了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有如此做 是你的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我承認
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的「偷窺錄像」和我的「植入違法芯片」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要雙方互不相讓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在現實世界中拚個兩敗俱傷麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎 能美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是超頻連接者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(466,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連接者有自己的解決方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(314,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想說 要對戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是超頻連接者這個稱呼 還是你的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(323,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都十分厭惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然是學長你的希望 那我也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也有個提案 行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提案？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正學長是想雙方戰鬥至點數全部失去為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正要打 不如就一戰定勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用學長喜歡的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無限制中立舞台 把對戰者的點數全部押上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏的一方就能獲得所有的點數和道具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這個一決勝負如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 事情已經發展成這樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在我發過去的是之後的交涉內容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美列出的條件列表
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs18\pos(511,157)\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&}決鬥條件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs15\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&\pos(402,272)}· 決鬥在無限制中立舞台進行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs15\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&\pos(467,288)}· 決鬥方法是雙方押上自己所有的超頻點數一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs18\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&\pos(499,314)}決鬥保證
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs15\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&\pos(656,399)}· 允許【小拓的虛擬角色名 犯懶了】同行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs15\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&\pos(654,416)}· 決鬥時間決定之前可以隨意更改或延遲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是接受這個申請的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無限制中立舞台的話 就有伏兵的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括允許我一同前往在內…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美 一定還有什麼勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 勝算有多大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以隨意更改對戰場所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現實而言 伏擊是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 能想到的 只有花大量的超頻點數
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是長時間潛伏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好 可能需要幾個月的忍耐力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個能美 有願意如此為他賣命的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有那樣的朋友在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美…就應該是個更加像樣的超頻連接者才對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(575,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 作為超頻連接者的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和利用加速的能美之間的對決
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們藉以立足的矜持 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接受決鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓 在學姐回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓一切結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決戰的時刻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:40.99,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(687,392)}Consolidation ; 羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}下集 Consolidation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}切開絕望的黑色光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}那是深刻羈絆的證明
